	"City Seeker" over .trait! "Cartographer" over .perk!
	122 over .specialtype! 0 over .specialmode! 1 over .female!
	2 4 rnd over .wits! 2 4 rnd over .attitude! 2 4 rnd over .composure! 6 over .loyalty!
	0 over .strength! 0 over .fitness! 0 over .shooting! 0 over .mechanical! 0 over .medical!

	"Carter" over .name!
	"fait toujours plus de cartes !" over .job!
	drop
;

